data.description: SELLER PROVIDING $10,000 TOWARD RATE BUY DOWN. This beautiful home is on a spacious oversized lot, at the end of a cul-de-sac in an established neighborhood with no HOA. You'll appreciate the above ground pool, deck and massive covered patio with outdoor TV and speakers when entertaining in the Texas heat. There is a fire pit for the winter months and several fruit trees and garden boxes for those with a green thumb. It is also perfect for families with pets due to the large pet door and chicken coop. Inside you'll find that the home has not only been painted all throughout but has also had a full kitchen remodel with brand new granite counter tops, cabinets, farm sink and high end appliances. The walk-in pantry is able to accommodate not only growing families but also avid cooks. This home is ideal for entertaining plenty of guests with its 5 bedrooms and 3 full baths. All of the bedrooms except one are conveniently located upstairs with a second living area, laundry/utility room and study nook. Downstairs the kitchen opens up to the breakfast area and living room with brick fireplace. There is also a flex room on the first floor that is perfect for an office, craft room, or formal dining area. And if you are looking for storage this house has an over abundance with coat closets, attic space and 2 outdoor storage sheds. The two car garage is also upgraded with work space for craftsmen and plenty of peg boards to store all of your tools. If you are looking for the perfect turn key home with all the amenities look no further. In the evening families are often out front playing in their yards, socializing with neighbors and watching their kids play. This home is not only within walking distance to Voss Farms Elementary but it is also close to Fischer Park, H-E-B, Walmart, restaurants and pharmacies. Come see how great this place is for yourself!
